metadata.name: Saddle Master
metadata.description:
Saddle mastery is a very old profession in Anatolia. Unfortunately, this profession, where only a few masters remain in Anatolia today, has unfortunately begun to be forgotten. In this photo I took in 2016, you see one of the few remaining saddle masters of Anatolia.

Artist : Mustafa Erbaş
Edition : 1 / 1
Resolution : 300 dpi
Size : 3648 x 4878
Location : Çorum / Türkiye
Camera : Canon 70D
Date : 28 / 05 / 2016
